Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.46,0:00:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name's Conan Edogawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.96,0:00:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,High school student Shinichi was forced\Nto take a drug that shrunk him!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.88,0:00:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although smaller, my mind remains\Nthat of a sharp detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.80,0:00:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's case is about amnesia!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.43,0:00:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A trap lurks in a\Nbeautiful woman's shadow!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.09,0:00:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can fool old Kogoro,\Nbut there's always only one truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.74,0:00:21.19,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The first end of the century in 100 years{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.83,0:00:27.41,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When told to cry, I laughed instead{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.03,0:00:39.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The first end of the century\Nin a long, long time{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.18,0:00:45.59,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We're leaping into a wide open world{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.17,0:00:52.18,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The things I tried to\Nunderstand as a child{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.34,0:00:58.61,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}remain a mystery even as an adult{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.89,0:01:04.61,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm neither a hotshot\Nnor especially great{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.89,0:01:11.03,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All I understand is\Nthe pounding of my heart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.19,0:01:16.92,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's neither an answer nor the truth{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.20,0:01:23.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All I have faith in is\Nthe pounding of my heart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.29,0:01:28.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That and nothing else {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.88,0:01:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Case of the Mysterious\NWoman with Amnesia.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.71,0:02:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Yuda Hitoshi, the murderer\Nwho was arrested
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.72,0:02:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,thanks to Mori Kogoro's\Nbrilliant detective work,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.67,0:02:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,escaped from Musashino Prison\Nlast night.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.20,0:02:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuda is an extremely\Ncalculating criminal,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.13,0:02:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and has many ingenious\Ntechniques at his disposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.42,0:02:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He murdered his wife Keiko-san to collect\Non her life insurance policy,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.88,0:02:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and was only arrested because of\NMori's incredible detective skills."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.55,0:02:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think we'll be alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.76,0:02:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.76,0:02:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you scared he'll want revenge?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.39,0:02:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revenge?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.64,0:02:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said so when he was arrested...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.90,0:02:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get you for this someday!\NMark my words, Mori Kogoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.40,0:02:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.77,0:03:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be fine, Ran!\NThere's nothing to worry about!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.57,0:03:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you be so relaxed about this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.74,0:03:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one he's after!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.16,0:03:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm probably the one he should\Nbe after, not the old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.71,0:03:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore you killed her, Yuda!\NGive yourself up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.71,0:03:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He worked so hard to escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.59,0:03:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wouldn't dare cause any trouble\Nthat would lead to his recapture!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.93,0:03:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's probably fleeing\Nthe country as we speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.26,0:03:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sure hope so...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.43,0:03:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, off to work I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.02,0:03:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.98,0:03:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where to?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.73,0:03:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You come too, Conan-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.09,0:03:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.31,0:03:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To protect Dad, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.15,0:03:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on out, I'm ready for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.08,0:03:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a break! Why did I have\Nto come here with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.14,0:04:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's he looking at?\NHe's not watching the race...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.15,0:04:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! Come on! Faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.31,0:04:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The old man?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.89,0:04:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me he's--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.89,0:04:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.11,0:04:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn. I hit you once and\Nall my luck goes down the drain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.36,0:04:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not nice to blame others.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.58,0:04:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My luck's back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.34,0:04:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.05,0:04:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My luck's not back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.31,0:04:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This lady has really developed muscles!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.48,0:05:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So she's not seriously injured?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.48,0:05:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really, except for one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.19,0:05:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All she can remember about herself\Nis that her name is Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.58,0:05:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.33,0:05:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Her memory?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.09,0:05:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Technically speaking, it's a light case\Nof retrograde amnesia.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.50,0:05:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Partial memory loss, in other words.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.17,0:05:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it happened when\Nshe fell off those stairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.01,0:05:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! It happened before that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.18,0:05:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was already out of it by then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.43,0:05:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then where?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.39,0:05:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will she get better?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.69,0:05:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.19,0:05:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it could happen tomorrow, in a month,\Nor even three years from now--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.90,0:05:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there's no way for us to know when.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.86,0:05:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's terrible...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.39,0:05:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! This calls\Nfor a great detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.12,0:05:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Mori Kogoro,\Nshall restore Maya-san's memory!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.41,0:05:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now. What does a great detective\Nhave to do with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.54,0:06:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi there! How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.54,0:06:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maya-san, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.42,0:06:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name's Mori. Mori Kogoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.43,0:06:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.61,0:06:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.30,0:06:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just relax and try to think back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.10,0:06:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you at least remember\Nwhere you lost your memory?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.15,0:06:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.15,0:06:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In your state, you couldn't\Nhave walked very far...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.48,0:06:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My deductions tell me that you must\Nhave lost your memory nearby...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.12,0:06:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anything\Nyou can almost remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.16,0:06:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look like you exercise,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.66,0:06:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so maybe you were\Non your way home from the gym!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.00,0:06:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gym?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.38,0:06:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You certainly are\Nincredibly proportioned!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.08,0:06:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surely you do some kind of sports,\Nlike body-building or weight-lifting!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.68,0:06:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her index fingers have scars on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.43,0:06:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does she do to get\Nthose kinds of scars?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.15,0:07:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, does your job involve\Nusing wires at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.73,0:07:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.41,0:07:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.16,0:07:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.74,0:07:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, my head! I can't\Nremember anything else!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.54,0:07:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.58,0:07:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan! Now look what you've done!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.96,0:07:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it looks like my luck has returned!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.43,0:07:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.93,0:07:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you really bring her memory back?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.81,0:07:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope. I haven't the slightest idea how.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.32,0:07:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.17,0:07:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, did you borrow this\Nfrom the lady at the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.10,0:07:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. That's all she had on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.24,0:07:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A puzzle piece and a page\Ntorn out of a book...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.32,0:07:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Gospel According to Matthew,\NChapter 5, Verse 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.37,0:07:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this from the Bible?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.41,0:08:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Bible?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.54,0:08:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Yeah, it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.75,0:08:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she's Christian.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.92,0:08:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Christian would tear up a bible?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.22,0:08:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I guess not.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.67,0:08:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means that--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.13,0:08:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she used it as a notepad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.05,0:08:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A notepad?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.38,0:08:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? There are light indentations\Non it that look like writing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.06,0:08:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.27,0:08:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, she must've written\Non the previous page
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.89,0:08:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and accidentally tore this page out\Nalong with the other one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.15,0:08:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"9.13, Last Supper"...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.04,0:08:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe this was a dinner date?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.04,0:08:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's gotta be it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.45,0:08:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But who with?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.16,0:08:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean "who with"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.42,0:08:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, that's a good question.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.38,0:08:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did she write this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.51,0:08:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It might be fastest to have her look\Nat something that identifies herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.93,0:09:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where might she unconsciously\Nuse a Bible to jot down some notes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.10,0:09:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see her writing in it while on\Nthe phone, then ripping the pages out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.15,0:09:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A hotel!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.22,0:09:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, hotels have Bibles\Nin all their rooms, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.05,0:09:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hotels?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.55,0:09:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I look at it,\Nthis is really nice paper!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.41,0:09:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nice and smooth\Nand really high quality!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.19,0:09:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! It would have to be\Nfrom at least a 3-star hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.73,0:09:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That narrows down the\Nnumber of possible hotels.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.90,0:09:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Dad! Let's check\Neach hotel one by one!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.07,0:09:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.82,0:09:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two are coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.61,0:09:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.01,0:09:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.35,0:09:41.81,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Yokoyama General Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.58,0:09:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you really be alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.22,0:09:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I even got the doctor's permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.91,0:09:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't ask you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.47,0:09:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.82,0:09:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to know\Nwho I am and where I'm from!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.22,0:09:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me come with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.14,0:10:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.81,0:10:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Using my detective skills,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.48,0:10:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've determined that this is a page\Nfrom a Bible in a high-class hotel!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.98,0:10:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soon I'll know which hotel\Nyou were staying at!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.24,0:10:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There'd be no suffering\Nif everything was that easy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.17,0:10:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Off to Mount View Hotel we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.95,0:10:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Dad! We're leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.45,0:10:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know if this young woman\Nhas been staying here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.33,0:10:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.05,0:10:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Might she be staying at this hotel?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.59,0:10:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, have you seen this lady before?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.44,0:10:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the 12th hotel now!\NI'm so exhausted!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.73,0:11:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, Tachibana-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.45,0:11:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know who she is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.08,0:11:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course. She's a guest here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.54,0:11:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tachibana Maya-sama.\NShe checked in two days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.96,0:11:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it, Maya-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.31,0:11:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bingo! This is the place!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.42,0:11:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, I'll search her things.\NYou two get out of the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.99,0:11:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.12,0:11:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing really here\Nto identify who you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.49,0:11:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you remember anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.34,0:11:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.04,0:11:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The address and phone number they\Nhave on record at the front desk
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.17,0:11:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,appear to be fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.57,0:12:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's no mistake that\NMaya-san was staying in this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.39,0:12:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What could...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.89,0:12:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not even sure\Nif that's my real name...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.81,0:12:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.52,0:12:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there something about that pendant?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.91,0:12:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My head! It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.26,0:12:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand this anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.78,0:12:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.89,0:12:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maya-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.24,0:12:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.04,0:12:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maya! Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.50,0:12:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.25,0:12:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is the man from the racetrack\Nafter Maya-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.68,0:13:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.53,0:13:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alright, Dad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.97,0:13:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?\NWhat was with that car?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.60,0:13:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.51,0:13:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maya-san! There's someone\Nout to get you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.11,0:13:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the shock of being attacked\Nmust've caused you to lose your memory!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.23,0:13:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where'd Conan-kun go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.24,0:13:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This area is full of\None-way streets and dead-ends!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.58,0:13:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I might be able to catch up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.87,0:13:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that predator-like look\Nthat Maya-san had...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.28,0:13:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She reacted almost like\Nshe knows when she's in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.74,0:13:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is she?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.54,0:13:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn it! I lost him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.41,0:13:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, what a mess...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.37,0:13:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it! You got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.31,0:13:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, officer! What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.31,0:13:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was there an accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.52,0:13:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of here, little boy.\NIt's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.52,0:13:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did the accident happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.35,0:13:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three hours ago. Now skedaddle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.20,0:14:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We found her at the crosswalk\Nnear 5th Street three hours ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.88,0:14:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not far from Beika Hotel!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.21,0:14:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.42,0:14:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she took the bus from\Nthe hotel, got in an accident,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.88,0:14:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then lost her memory from the shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.34,0:14:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then she walked in a daze\Nto the pedestrian bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.56,0:14:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bus! A truck!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.98,0:14:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And a collision?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.57,0:14:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember! I remember now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.57,0:14:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Way to go, Conan-kun! You did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.95,0:14:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was just luck, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.11,0:14:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why did she leave after that\Nwithout getting any medical treatment?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.96,0:14:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe because that man\Nwas trying to get her?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.46,0:14:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So despite having lost her memory,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.30,0:15:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she instinctually ran away from danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.12,0:15:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, let's take a ride on the bus!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.30,0:15:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! You might remember\Nwhere you were planning to go
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.56,0:15:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if the accident hadn't happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.96,0:15:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.54,0:15:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't remember anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.00,0:15:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't rush yourself. You've already\Nremembered a lot in one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.36,0:15:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But with all the people\Ngetting on and off,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.72,0:15:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,nobody will remember her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.55,0:15:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't leave any tracks to follow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.39,0:15:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it! I was supposed\Nto get off here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.23,0:16:03.19,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Gas Tank
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.82,0:16:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's walk around for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.20,0:16:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.63,0:16:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maya-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.60,0:16:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me these two are--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.82,0:16:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's piano wire doing there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.03,0:16:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell? Are you\Ntrying to kill us all?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.86,0:16:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.44,0:16:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.41,0:16:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.70,0:16:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both the time at the hotel and now...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.16,0:16:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Judging from the timing, he's not\Ntrying to kill her or even all of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.34,0:16:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's after old man Kogoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.70,0:16:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran-neechan! Stay with Maya-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.38,0:16:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, where are you--?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.59,0:17:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My head!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.72,0:17:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.71,0:17:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you should rest somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.42,0:17:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.93,0:17:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he's out to kill Kogoro,\Nthen he must be--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.40,0:17:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad! Maya-san's gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.07,0:17:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you two doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.44,0:17:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it obvious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.73,0:17:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.57,0:17:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We owe you one...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.57,0:17:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We owe you one...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.12,0:17:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bad news! Maya-san disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.29,0:17:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I only looked away\Nfor a second, but--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.08,0:17:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where could she have gone though?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.24,0:17:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a chance that man got her!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.13,0:17:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's highly doubtful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.54,0:17:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But maybe she made herself disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.54,0:17:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she got her memory back...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.97,0:17:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, let's look for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.43,0:17:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two go that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.73,0:17:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.39,0:17:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Conan-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.26,0:18:00.27,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Last Supper
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.68,0:18:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! Thanks to that woman,\Nmy plan's been ruined...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.75,0:18:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the target.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.29,0:18:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.47,0:18:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to watch him\Nsuffer and die, but no!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.48,0:18:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want anyone getting in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.16,0:18:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maya-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.57,0:18:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember now! That man's\Nhideout is over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.01,0:18:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.35,0:18:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...9th Street, building #13!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.62,0:19:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe those numbers written\Nin that Bible were an address!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.62,0:19:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means that's the place!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.17,0:19:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what "Last Supper"\Nreferred to!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.55,0:19:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuda! So it was him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.35,0:19:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it was Dad he was after?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.77,0:19:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Last Supper...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.19,0:19:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that puzzle piece\Nwas part of this picture!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.85,0:19:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's been here too, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.20,0:19:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who in the world is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.74,0:19:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is she involved with this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.74,0:19:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.99,0:19:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuda's puzzle piece was the key\Nto information about Kogoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.54,0:19:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, she came here\Nto get it from him...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.79,0:19:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it! Now I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.34,0:19:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran-neechan! Call the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.80,0:19:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.42,0:19:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you find out where\Nhis hideout was, Maya-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.52,0:20:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuda and Maya-san\Nclearly knew each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.52,0:20:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who exactly is she?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.57,0:20:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get you for this someday!\NMark my words!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.57,0:20:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her well-trained body\Nand sharp reflexes...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.24,0:20:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then that wire she pulled out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.45,0:20:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she used a bus instead\Nof a taxi or rental car
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.12,0:20:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to hide her tracks\Nlike most professionals do,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.29,0:20:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then there's no mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.45,0:20:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a professional killer\Nthat Yuda hired to take Kogoro out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.02,0:20:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty sure he came this way...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.98,0:20:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.41,0:21:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.54,0:21:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your memory returned when Yuda\Ndropped the concrete on us, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.34,0:21:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! My memory\Ncame back because of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.00,0:21:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should really thank him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.09,0:21:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should've realized when you tried\Nto hide the marks on your hands
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.26,0:21:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,at the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.76,0:21:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Realized that you were an assassin\Nwho uses piano wire, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.60,0:21:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just figuring out that I use wire\Nfor a living was impressive enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.73,0:21:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who exactly are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.61,0:21:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan Edogawa. A detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.57,0:21:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A detective?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.03,0:21:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.78,0:21:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alright?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.51,0:21:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world just happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.28,0:21:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would seem I've lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.01,0:22:11.43,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just my imagination {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.56,0:22:21.19,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Playing with threads around my finger\Nwhile drinking lukewarm tea{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.90,0:22:30.24,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's walk lightly\Nto the bossa nova rhythm{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.37,0:22:35.25,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The puzzle pieces are in my hands{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.46,0:22:41.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.67,0:22:51.39,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was in the same place last week\Nbut with different clothes{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.72,0:22:58.81,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Step by step,\Nthere's no reason to be anxious{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.73,0:23:05.23,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Case by case,\NI don't care if you laugh{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.65,0:23:14.99,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Beyond the countless days,\Nshe's waiting for me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.41,0:23:19.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I gotta go my own way {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.97,0:23:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems both he and I chose\Nthe wrong target, little detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.43,0:23:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.26,0:23:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did she say?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.59,0:23:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, she was saying that Mori Kogoro\Nreally is a great detective
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.65,0:23:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,since he captured\Nthe same guy twice in a row!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.19,0:23:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like luck is on your side again!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.53,0:23:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.45,0:23:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess that means I'll be raking it in\Nafter this next G1 horse race then!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.05,0:24:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, please explain\Nthe situation during the kidnapping.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.64,0:24:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to think\Nabout Naoko being dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.26,0:24:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a famous corporate raider.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.75,0:24:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you haven't garnered\Na lot of hatred in your time?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.10,0:24:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want your lousy money.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.15,0:24:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can keep it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.21,0:24:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.51,0:24:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think he would be happy,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.18,0:24:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even if he were avenged.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.26,0:24:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next Conan--
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.76,0:24:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Fake Ransom Case.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.23,0:24:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's Hint:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.48,0:24:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scuba set.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.34,0:24:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode's culprit will be tough to identify.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.55,0:24:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Glub, glub, glub.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.88,0:24:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
